OL,3,CClosure of small channels in the
OL,4,Cdebate about linear TV's future
OL,6,GI often do something of an
OL,7,Gimpersonation of Mark Twain. Reports,
OL,8,GI argue, of the death of linear TV are
OL,9,Gexaggerated.
OL,11,FOf course there is an important
OL,12,Fqualification here.
OL,14,FI make a complete distinction between
OL,15,Fmajor channels like BBC One and ITV 1
OL,16,Fand smaller channels ` especially
OL,17,Fniche channels.
OL,19,FThis week came news of the closure of
OL,20,Fa few niche linear services. It will
OL,21,Fsoon be goodbye to Tiny Pop and
OL,22,FChannel 4's suite of music channels.
