OL,4,Cdebate about linear TV's future
OL,6,FChannel 4 has also said it may close
OL,7,Fother channels in the future and
OL,8,Fregards itself as "ahead of the curve"
OL,9,Fon the move online.
OL,11,FThere's no need to lose sleep over
OL,12,Fsmall commercial channels. It's quite
OL,13,Fsimple ` if a channel isn't making
OL,14,Fmoney it has no future, just like any
OL,15,Fother business.
