OL,4,Cdebate about linear TV's future
OL,6,FChannel 4 has always regarded its
OL,7,Fbroader suite of channels as
OL,8,Fcommercial operations ` even though,
OL,9,Ffor instance, Film4 retains the
OL,10,Fcapacity to surprise with some of its
OL,11,Fchoices and More4 includes some
OL,12,Fthoughtful material.
OL,14,FThe inevitable question is how much
OL,15,Flonger they will survive for as linear
OL,16,Fservices.
OL,18,FIf I were a betting man, I would
OL,19,Fsuggest the two of Channel 4's spin-
OL,20,Foff channels which are likely to
OL,21,Fdisappear first are 4Seven and E4
OL,22,FExtra.
