OL,6,FBoth get modest ratings and are
OL,7,Fbroadcast on commercial capacity on
OL,8,FFreeview ` not Channel 4's gifted
OL,9,Fspace.
OL,11,FChannel 4 has particular reasons for
OL,12,Fbeing keen to focus on on-demand. It
OL,13,Fhas particular responsibilities
OL,14,Ftowards the young.
OL,16,FChannel 4 itself doesn't have the
OL,17,Fspecial ability of the BBC and ITV 1
OL,18,Fto bring disparate groups of people
OL,19,Ftogether ` historically, its very
OL,20,Fpoint was to serve the audience as
OL,21,Findividuals.
