OL,6,FOfcom is considering whether to allow
OL,7,FChannel 4 to focus its resources on a
OL,8,Fsmaller number of commissions which
OL,9,Fmake more impact.
OL,11,FI really cannot imagine Channel 4
OL,12,Fceasing to exist as a linear service
OL,13,Fin the foreseeable future even if we
OL,14,Fare likely to continue to see more and
OL,15,Fmore of its content appearing on-
OL,16,Fdemand first.
OL,18,FAnd with the spin-off channels, it'll
OL,19,Fdepend on money. When they
OL,20,Fconsistently lose money it will be bye
OL,21,Fbye.
