OL,3,CClosure of small channels in the
OL,4,Cdebate about linear TV's future
OL,6,FOf course, there is no doubt the
OL,7,Fnumber of linear services will
OL,8,Fcontinue to thin out: the BBC is still
OL,9,Fexpected to close BBC Four and CBBC as
OL,10,Flinear services at some point soon
OL,11,Falthough no date has been announced.
OL,13,FIn a funny kind of way though, might
OL,14,Fhaving fewer linear channels help
OL,15,Fprotect the major ones?
OL,17,FIf you have fewer channels to choose
OL,18,Fbetween, might some people simply
OL,19,Fwatch more on those which remain?
