OL,6,FIncidentally it was interesting to
OL,7,Fnote the concerns of some MPs over the
OL,8,Ffuture of Freeview ` it's role in
OL,9,Fareas where the quality of reliability
OL,10,Fof broadband is unsatisfactory should
OL,11,Fnot be understated.
OL,13,FPersonally though I am relaxed about
OL,14,Fthe threat of closure.
OL,16,FAs long as it is watched by a
OL,17,Fsignificant proportion of the audience
OL,18,Fit will be safe.
