OL,6,FAny move online would require years of
OL,7,Fwork ` a huge amount of support would
OL,8,Fneed to be offered to people who don't
OL,9,Fuse the internet or live in areas with
OL,10,Finadequate internet coverage. It will
OL,11,Fbe interesting to see whether Freely `
OL,12,Fthe new way of watching TV online `
OL,13,Ftakes off.
OL,15,FFor now, any prospect of "turning off
OL,16,FTV" would be a guaranteed vote loser.
