OL,6,FYou only need to look at the BBC's
OL,7,Fcaution over closing Radio 4 LW
OL,8,F(although separate programmes end
OL,9,Fshortly) and 5 Live MW to realise how
OL,10,Fa public service broadcaster must take
OL,11,Faccessibility seriously.
OL,13,FStill let's make a distinction between
OL,14,Flinear channels and how they are
OL,15,Fdistributed ` if DTT is superseded,
OL,16,Fthat is no different to the end of 405-
OL,17,Fline or UHF analogue.
